{"tid":1562962,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"要繼續舉美國旗！","createTime":"2019-09-12T08:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T10:58:08.000Z","uid":182274,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6d3c4ef97a11ff13f6e329db512c7916aa1f8989","tid":1562962,"uid":182274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:25:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/700268879/posts/10157187675233880?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F700268879%2Fposts%2F10157187675233880%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2Fbe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=72e0212a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/700268879/posts/10157187675233880?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n據聞美國只需一位參議員提出senate hold，只要全體不足三分二反對，香港人權及民主法案即可在參議會上無限期擱置，直至有關議員收回動議。<br />\n<br />\n假如屬實，中國將全力收買部份參議員，企圖促成法案流產。與此同時，在香港營造萬人普天同慶唱流行曲的氣氛，將上周高舉美國國旗、唱美國國歌的勢頭消散於無形。只要香港人不再強烈請求美國支援，而香港事態不會影響美國的民主，美國將不會有動力以狠辣的法案監察香港。屆時，民意代表泛民議員將有充分的理由建議美國減辣，以免在局勢緩和的時候傷害香港經濟。<br />\n<br />\n只要未來兩周，香港人繼續以所謂香港國歌取代美國國歌的話，將美國角色隱沒至大後方的話，美國減辣的機會相當高。要保持辣度，必需仰賴美國議員極具說服力論證，非常困難。香港人將自己的好牌一張張的送出，無話可說。<br />\n<br />\n唱還唱 都要繼續比美國知道we need help <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人加油 ！"},{"pid":"3c491b10e26e6d2cccbd5c138180180bdb1f4e24","tid":1562962,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:27:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"e4e631428a9db691fca85096b9f46f594398c716","tid":1562962,"uid":182274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:33:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1a9c8b0accc5ee08dd529c6fce0f9f76b2224a98","tid":1562962,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:34:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"11d1c3ea3b34fa0a3ba8b11e21714ed540e8a2c9","tid":1562962,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:35:39.000Z","msg":"要唱埋歌<br />\n唔搵野拉美國埋黎 佢話走就走架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b303f1e00f431a51b798b0afa5be754942a710","tid":1562962,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:39:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed00f5a95d1fda4894becd1a89d59390f653ca8","tid":1562962,"uid":276971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59494f3f2161580979cca41d3a2140ed742a3f95","tid":1562962,"uid":182274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:48:21.000Z","msg":"而家晚晚都唱願榮光歸香港 唔知會唔會比美國感覺我地贏左咁唔需要援助 (雖然我每次聽都唱都好感動） 但一日未過法案一日都未贏！所以要保持初心！繼續出黎同埋做文宣 係twitter比美國佬見到"},{"pid":"092dcef70a736850009b5a54625d334d494b1d2a","tid":1562962,"uid":82482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:06:14.000Z","msg":"首先美國會議員被中共收賣的可能性相當低<br />\n<br />\n因為美國的政府情報組織係全球頂尖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二係,如果舉國旗唱美國國歌可以左右到美議員的決定,大家未免太低估佢地<br />\n<br />\n有一點反而同意,希望各界俾到議員睇到,香港人係好樂意港共官員被制裁,但係是透過遊行,文宣等進行<br />\n<br />\n最後係,中共似乎寧願香港人唱美國國歌,都不要唱港獨意味的願榮耀歸香港,呢個係兩害取其輕,亦都係facebook之所以有此類文章的原意<br />\n<br />\n大概係中共的文宣"},{"pid":"b9e5e9d4af7f09e0169162854b5252e3d9248318","tid":1562962,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:58:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}